{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"2":"Prayer (Kitab Al-Salat)"},"section_detail":{"2":{"hadithnumber_first":391,"hadithnumber_last":1160,"arabicnumber_first":391,"arabicnumber_last":1160}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":850,"arabicnumber":850,"text":"Rapporté par Abdullah ibn Abbas : Le Prophète ﷺ disait entre les deux prosternations : « Ô Allah, pardonne-moi, fais-moi miséricorde, guide-moi, guéris-moi et accorde-moi ma subsistance. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":2,"hadith":460}}]}